{"tid":885040,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中銀香港入得未?","createTime":"2018-11-01T05:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T15:10:57.000Z","uid":169618,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0f604cb991c8d72d13c74ba08a51ee88726d17bb","tid":885040,"uid":169618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"由高位跌咗 $10, 之前唔知邊個有巴打話會到 $28, 都差唔多了, 入得未?<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 知道呢種自 high post 實有巴打屌, 不過一直想入銀行股又討厭獅子..."},{"pid":"144520b1a68f4d360a6c18ffbc95b7b2d4c4ed95","tid":885040,"uid":219432,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"銀行股呢排被沽得咁狠, 事出必有因, 可能有春江鴨預視了未來一些因素....<br />\n不如掉返轉頭諗, 本地銀行之前為何業積亮麗, 由何種業務帶動, 咁樣可能會找出一些頭緒....!"},{"pid":"f0645254a6fa95d793c687e67b606ce002e0d03a","tid":885040,"uid":37063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"無岩定錯 無人保證搵到最低位<br />\n分段入最理性"},{"pid":"4e63ef8f09e6d065d492f8a017a1d506450ff971","tid":885040,"uid":69895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"原因係樓跌帶動按揭大插，我覺得未反映完，打算33蚊就put佢"},{"pid":"4304ab603da8cf12365b6d7057b9e24c7aa33c13","tid":885040,"uid":109072,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"入得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.RSI1去到個位數字 代表佢嚴重超賣 <br />\n2.留意沽空 呢幾日keep住15%樓下 下行壓力細左好多(15-18/10keep住30%以上)<br />\n3.大行放業績前一致唱好 2388步入十月前一直跑贏大市 <br />\n4.一放業績就夾埋一齊調低目標價 你班老散就驚到賤賣<br />\n5.一直2388都淨係得一隻認沽 跟本冇咩比機會你short<br />\n6.遲多幾個星期又會炒加息 話咩柒淨息差<br />\n結論: 大行唱想水鳩你班散戶高位入貨 自己就借貨沽 呢排一大跌完就平倉 去到$29就大手補返貨 你班友已經冇貨 好今日就開始升返 短線睇上返$33<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發夢諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ac7a9f6a8c76189ff90bebabcf9f21d478a78b","tid":885040,"uid":162526,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"樓爆仲買銀行股？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我由39走得翻幾手"},{"pid":"5c766ef9d0ca0f7566bcb225b187a717adcd7a08","tid":885040,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ac7a9f6a8c76189ff90bebabcf9f21d478a78b","tid":885040,"uid":162526,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"樓爆仲買銀行股？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我由39走得翻幾手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T23:27:01.000Z","msg":"根本2字頭就大特價時段<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好股平賣<br />\n<br />\n反而5仔就真係有暗湧 自己好睇路啦"},{"pid":"a085814bd1fd49f7eabe89a58e2dba126353f6cc","tid":885040,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T23:41:46.000Z","msg":"All in 保平安"},{"pid":"450a681eab24dfb03f8d2625befcd506b9608f0c","tid":885040,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陣間入少少試下水溫先 睇短線都好"},{"pid":"4d50d8a33e6f84092134e4331fa39bedd38e1760","tid":885040,"uid":169008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"星期一升呀！"},{"pid":"f702578dc7a65df52435b9193e0a44235c6226cf","tid":885040,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T16:55:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92b406eea3b51b357e96c5c608b826dc894fba57","tid":885040,"uid":169618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"星期五排 $30 入唔到，可能想今日等埋我"},{"pid":"818006f73eafdb8ba28f2941beec9bb2b7cec89d","tid":885040,"uid":169008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"大家點睇"},{"pid":"39a333fd2147e83fd3fdd922e00f4b5d1ec0b935","tid":885040,"uid":169618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"818006f73eafdb8ba28f2941beec9bb2b7cec89d","tid":885040,"uid":169008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"